```cpp
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int x=1;
int main(){
	int k;
	cin>>k;
	for(int i=10000;i<=30000;i++){
		if((i/100)%k==0&&(i/10%1000)%k==0&&(i%1000)%k==0){
			cout<<i<<endl;
			x=0;
		} 
	}
	if(x==1) cout<<"No"<<endl;
}
```
